f893b8ea3d5cb259b00451.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F123617_02c9b33b74f893b8ea3d5cb259b00451.png&h=cf320b5d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係要去到PhD 咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816831f5811328122801361ca61f2806b848f42d","tid":548833,"uid":96721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"你係咪係美國呀？係就不如留低最少兩三年先走啦，返香港無經驗好難搞<br />\n<br />\n不過現時呢行其實開始飽和，好多大公司都唔太需要新人。細公司又通常想即食，想請有經驗既。如果你有 intern 經驗，會好好多<br />\n<br />\n好多公司逐步將 data science projects 變做automated，而 automation 呢步俾唔少前人做好晒啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非 data scientist，但工作上經常要同 data scientist 合作"},{"pid":"e32f4c4f820998261cb77c10c506376c171fa1c6","tid":548833,"uid":163739,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"香港唔使諗啦，除左少數（外資）公司，好多腦細唔會覺得自己要用到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a722a66b34d99e1a3130052d81e651f54f8a1fca","tid":548833,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e32f4c4f820998261cb77c10c506376c171fa1c6","tid":548833,"uid":163739,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"香港唔使諗啦，除左少數（外資）公司，好多腦細唔會覺得自己要用到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"正正係因為香港冇人材, 要呢啲位的公司會比好高人工"},{"pid":"07ecbf2aa6efd04c3baa