\" />"},{"pid":"60ed2ea0e83d1984f1c85ee814453c12c5e93e33","tid":548833,"uid":170252,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時黎講，個人覺得市場唔成熟。好多公司都系度出post穩人。 但唔少系要master /phd，仲要十項全能。認真,如果全部fulfil ,全香港可能得二三十人合資格。見到d post真系想hi個hr。佢地好想穩一個即刻用得既人去做，但香港根本無準備過，點會有人。公司前一排，系出過post (requirement合理個種)，但掛左幾個月無乜respond 。<br />\n公司黎講(不只我自己宜家公司)，好多老闆(尤其大老闆)淨系知道big data, ai, machine learning,但系對做到d乜,有乜嘢需要準備，全部一概唔知道，完全無準備過個database。就算請到data scientist,個data scientist 全部project 要由automation 做起，嗮錢嗮時間。情況就好似前面ching講禁樣。<br />\n<br />\nps :宜家做緊里行嘅一個小學雞"},{"pid":"e565b6d42bbaa203441ccc6d271fb4a60c3e2d48","tid":548833,"uid":89240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"D老闆話係香港DA要摸石過河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d8d8b041ecd2749ef2b10595703e3f251c760e","tid":548833,"uid":89240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D老闆話係香港<span style=\"color: red;\">做</span>DA要摸石過河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"defa13e51cf9dd1c283830b7b77736696892cc65","tid":548833,"uid":170252,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ec15508c295a8b650dfb7d1658c150985a502ddc","tid":548833,"uid":110163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"816831f5811328122801361ca61f2806b848f42d","tid":548833,"uid":96721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"你係咪係美國呀？係就不如留低最少兩三年先走啦，返香港無經驗好難搞<br />\n<br />\n不過現時呢行其實開始飽和，好多大公司都唔太需要新人。細公司又通常想即食，想請有經驗既。如果你有 intern 經驗，會好好多<br />\n<br />\n好多公司逐步將 data science projects 變做automated，而 automation 呢步俾唔少前人做好晒啦 <im